Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Intelligent computers
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wzvj
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Apr 1983
Intelligent computers - looking to a future of seriously smart machines. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.